name: CoreAPI Deployment_Transfer
description: API to access results of Planet 9 Deployment_Transfer details.
about:
Description

Planet 9-Deployment transfer maintains the list of all Systems and routes transfer requests.

API Deployment_Transfer is the Planet 9 API to access the API's of Deployment- Transfer, and the operations performed on them.

Operations Performed 

Systems/List

Get all the Systems- List 

ResponseSystemsList(array) - Definition


Deploy/List

Get all the Routes - List 

ResponseDeployList(array) - Definition


Deploy/Get

Get the Deployed object

RequestID
ResponseGet(object)-Definition                         


Deploy/SetStatus

Set status of Transfer(Approve/Reject)

RequestID
ResponseSetStatus(object)
